songs.title: 5 Star*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics from Snippet

[Verse: Comethazine]
I been strapped with the toolie (Gang)
Roll him like sushi if he try to do me (Come here)
Then dip in the two seat, smokin' on a doobie (Yeah)
Right hand to God, bitch, I don't fuck with losin' (No)
Nigga run up, now you know what I'm doin'
I just told you in them last two bars
Dropped out of school, still bought two cars (Bitch)
Me and my bitch hit the five star (Yeah), that's two stars (Yeah)
I can see the paparazzi from afar (Yeah)
Shoot a fuck nigga in his cheekbone
Last thing he seen was a green beam aimed at his jaw (Boom)
